snippet.title: Russell Brand
snippet.description:
Welcome to my YouTube channel!

Everybody knows that the old ideas won’t help us. Religion is dead. Capitalism is dead. Communism is dead. Where will the answers of the next century lie? Particularly, when we’re facing a mental health epidemic and ecological melt down. 

On this channel my videos explore new ways to connect with ourselves and one another and how to elevate our consciousness.

REVELATION: my new audible original is out NOW - You can get it here:

US: http://adbl.co/revelation
UK: http://adbl.co/revelationuk
AU: http://adbl.co/revelationau
CA: http://adbl.co/revelationca

I'd love you to subscribe to my channel, oh and make sure to hit that notification bell otherwise you won't get told about new videos!

Love,
Russell
X
